      "firm_id": "optimistic_5",
      "description": "Get ready to hit the road in this reliable and budget-friendly ride! While it shows some honest signs of its journey through the years, including some cosmetic wear and tear, it remains a sturdy and dependable vehicle that\u2019s ready for many more miles. This is a fantastic opportunity to own a functional, well-loved car at a price that offers incredible value!",
